  "title": "Cloud Security Engineer – AWS Platforms",
  "description": "<p>We are seeking an experienced AWS Security Engineer to support the design, implementation, and operation of secure, enterprise-scale AWS environments. This role focuses on embedding security best practices across cloud infrastructure and supporting cloud deployments in regulated and mission-critical environments.</p><h3>Key Responsibilities</h3><p><ul><li>Design, implement, and operate secure AWS cloud infrastructure.</li><li>Configure and manage AWS security services including IAM, VPC security, logging, and monitoring.</li><li>Enforce cloud security best practices across compute, storage, and networking.</li><li>Support cloud project delivery with strong governance and compliance controls.</li><li>Perform security hardening, reviews, and remediation for AWS workloads.</li><li>Implement automation and Infrastructure-as-Code to enhance security and consistency.</li><li>Collaborate with engineering and operations teams to improve cloud security posture.</li></ul></p><h3>Requirements</h3><p><ul><li>Proven experience managing AWS environments at scale with a security focus.</li><li>Strong hands-on knowledge of EC2, S3, VPC, Lambda, RDS, IAM, and CloudWatch.</li><li>Good understanding of AWS networking, security controls, and identity management.</li><li>Experience operating in enterprise or regulated environments.</li><li>Strong problem-solving and communication skills.</li><li>AWS certifications are highly desirable.</li><li>Experience with IaC / automation tools (CloudFormation, Terraform, Ansible) is an advantage.</li><li>Exposure to Docker and Kubernetes security is a plus.</li><li>Singaporeans Only</li></ul></p><p><strong>To Apply</strong><br />To apply or find out more information on this role, please email us or send in your updated resume to:<br /><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">lynn.tay@starcareerconsulting.com</a></p><p><strong>Lynn Tay</strong> (Reg. No. R1876711)<br /><strong>STAR CAREER CONSULTING PTE LTD</strong> (EA Licence: 20C0353)</p>",
